{"tid":722011,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港安老服務業前景堪憂","createTime":"2018-06-29T06:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T10:40:33.000Z","uid":79353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f66331dc0237bc52abbfc7e760cd3b56ee847b0","tid":722011,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:39:35.000Z","msg":"當你發現負責派藥嘅保健員全部都係廣東話講唔正嘅大陸人，呢啲已經叫有中學學歷。<br />\n<br />\n當你發現做前線護理嘅全部都係大陸村姑，真係由大陸不知名農村出城做野。雖然呢班係俾私營院舍剝削得最嚴重嘅一班員工。<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲賤種，夏天三十幾度嘅下午熱到痴撚線。佢自己喺房開大個冷氣玩電話。老人家喺廳睇電視就唔可以開冷氣。真係屌你老味正賤種。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92813e3f737b6046a2ce3b7dc8528c91d8b41fd7","tid":722011,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:49:29.000Z","msg":"蘋果幫到你"},{"pid":"9c4b0b29f487f865e33bd97063195c6a80b6e91c","tid":722011,"uid":147871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92813e3f737b6046a2ce3b7dc8528c91d8b41fd7","tid":722011,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:49:29.000Z","msg":"蘋果幫到你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76508260e98a4ebbd00d23134ef2c000c966da71","tid":722011,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"一句：你會唔會去做護理行業？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答案一早有。"},{"pid":"704b03ddc9a0dbf6759f383dd5e66bdf35eb05cf","tid":722011,"uid":138809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76508260e98a4ebbd00d23134ef2c000c966da71","tid":722011,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"一句：你會唔會去做護理行業？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答案一早有。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T07:00:43.000Z","msg":"nursing"},{"pid":"8d4bc1defda9b3b1b8fa2db